# PropertyForSale - Prompt Log

## Session: 2026-04-04

### Initial Project Request

We are going to build a brand new application with these characteristics:

1.  A nix flake that provides the development environment and also provides a
    nixosanywhere framework for deploying onto a hetzner server, running the
    site behind nginx with a certbot certificate and great security profile etc.
2.  A web application written in go with a really nicely laid out backend
    structure - using whatever the best go equivalent to pythons django framework
    would be.
3.  The web frontend written in reactjs and chakra css with the most
    awe-inspiring css focussed around selling a property you can imagine.
4.  Integrated map support using map lire
5.  Support for 3d video play throughs that the user can interact with.
6.  Support for viewing architectural house plans in 2d and 3d models (generated
    from an autocad or similar file)
7.  A landing page with key high level selling points (location, prince range,
    summary, enticement pics)
8.  A login using social auth using popular platforms including apple, github,
    microsoft, github, facebook, etc.
9.  Detailed backend analytics including a map that resolves ip addresses of
    visitors to locations, dwell times, most popular information that people want
    to access, exit points with insights into what prompts people to move.
10. AB testing of each content section with writing in different styles and
    levels of content detail. Also presenting this in terms of how pricing is presented.
11. SEO and adwords campaign planning and management.
12. Notifications of experssions of interests, daily performance summaries.
13. A versioned content management system which lets you see the difference and
    author of each change, rollbacks, etc. It should also let you upload media
    including photos, videos, 3d videos, pdfs, sounds files.
14. A guided page builder that walks you through the whole framework of building
    the promotional site for a property. This will work in a heirachical way
    eg. Define a property, add a dwelling or building, add rooms, add property areas
    e.g. gardens or fields. etc. Each of these items should be able to have one or
    more media files attached and if there is a sound file this should be able to be
    set to autoplay when the user enters the information component. e.g. they enter
    the garden view and we play ambient sounds from the garden. It should be
    possible to navigate the property through an interactive localised map using
    maplibre with hyperlinked features e.g. clicking on a dwelling takes you to the
    dwelling sub page.

