- Imported and rendered Map3DTab component
- Removed ZIP handling from MediaTab (now shows info toast directing to 3D Map tab)
- Removed .zip from file input accept attribute
- Removed scene3d badge from media grid (now in dedicated tab)

#### Tests (pkg/ziputil/ziputil_test.go)
